records.name: Sun Siyam Vilu Reef With Free Transfer

descriptions.direction: Located in Vilu Reef, Sun Siyam Vilu Reef is on the beach. Meedhoo Harbour and Vommuli Pier are worth checking out if an activity is on the agenda, while those wishing to experience the area's natural beauty can explore Meedhuffushi Island Beach and Kandima Beach. With windsurfing and fishing nearby, you'll find plenty of adventures in the water.
descriptions.general: This superb resort is located on one of many paradisiacal islands that make up the Maldives and is ideal for a romantic getaway. Accessed by a 40-minute seaplane flight in which guests can truly discover the beauty of the area from the air, this excellent resort features three types of modern villas in peaceful and relaxing surroundings. Those most demanding visitors may prefer the top of the range Presidential Suite which features traditional Maldivian décor, custom-made furnishings and modern amenities to cater for every need. Meanwhile, a multitude of leisure activities are available including snorkelling around the natural reefs and trips to local untouched islands. The spa area is the best place to rejuvenate body and mind thanks to flower baths and Ayurvedic rituals.
